          Find out more information: http://www.st.com/st25dvFor our free SW: http://www.st.com/st25appTo order one of our ST25DV-discovery kits http://www.st.com/st25dv-di...In this video Damien will show you how developers like you can use the ST25DV dynamic tags to solve real-life industrial problems.Adding a ST25DV tag on a device offers a way for the I2C bus of a microcontroller to communicate with the external world via an RF interface and Damien will show you how to get yourself setup to run an inventory and to program your electronic devices on the production line.Applications include:  detecting switched off items, tagging items for certain configurations, running inventories and so on
          
